features: 𝗣𝗼𝘄𝗲𝗿𝗳𝘂𝗹 𝟰𝟴,𝟬𝟬𝟬 𝗕𝗧𝗨 𝗛𝗲𝗮𝘁: Our outdoor patio heater measures 48,000 BTU to spread heat up to an 18-foot diameter from its central heating position. With ETL certification, it is ideal for outdoor and commercial use, and can be placed in an outdoor balcony, garden, swimming pool, etc.

𝗠𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗗𝘂𝗿𝗮𝗯𝗹𝗲 𝗗𝗼𝘂𝗯𝗹𝗲-𝗹𝗮𝘆𝗲𝗿 𝗛𝗲𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗠𝗲𝘀𝗵: High-quality 304 stainless steel is used in our double-cover heating mesh design. Compared with a traditional single layer burning mesh heater, the EAST OAK Outdoor Heater is stronger, more durable, and safer, and the service life is improved by 20%.

𝗦𝗮𝗳𝗲𝘁𝘆 𝗣𝗿𝗼𝘁𝗲𝗰𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗦𝘆𝘀𝘁𝗲𝗺: The Tip-over Protection system will shut off the flame when the patio heater propane is tilted more than 45 degrees. If the flame goes out, the Flame-out Protection system automatically shuts off the gas supply.

𝗣𝗮𝘁𝗲𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗱 𝗥𝗼𝘂𝗻𝗱 𝗧𝗮𝗯𝗹𝗲 𝗗𝗲𝘀𝗶𝗴𝗻: The Propane Heater features a unique round propane tank lid that allows you to place snacks, drinks, cell phones, or other small objects on top. Our barrel has a hole design, so you can reach directly in and turn off the heater, which is very convenient.

𝗙𝗮𝘀𝘁 𝟱-𝘀𝗲𝗰𝗼𝗻𝗱 𝗜𝗴𝗻𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻, 𝗘𝗮𝘀𝘆 𝗧𝗼 𝗢𝗽𝗲𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗲: The Patio Heater is easy to be start with a one-touch ignition system which can light the flame in under five seconds. The adjustable control knob can customize the heat from low to high or turn off the heater.
𝟯-𝗬𝗲𝗮𝗿 𝗖𝗨𝗦𝗧𝗢𝗠𝗘𝗥 𝗦𝗨𝗣𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧: EAST OAK promises lifetime customer support and 3 years quality assurance.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well built easy assembly
reviews.reviewText: Product came with extremely clear instructions in a glossily full color instruction manual. Parts were clearly identified and mounted on a vacuum packed card with an extra fastener for each one. All holes lined upped perfectly. Without a doubt the best assemble yourself product I have seen in years. Works wonderfully being easy to light and excellent heat output. Took less than an hour to assemble and a first class product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love the HEAT
reviews.reviewText: Love the heat this thing puts off. It was economical, east to put together and lightweight enough to move around. Great product! Especially for the price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble, looks modern
reviews.reviewText: Super happy with the lamp, very easily to build, almost dummy-proof. All instructions were easy to understand AKA written in English so that was nice. Puts out a ton of heat also! Only issue I had was I ordered this during black friday and it got pawned to UPS which blamed so and so and lost the package and blah blah blah so I said I needed a replacement and it came decently quick but once the product showed up I was pretty happy cause it works well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars The burner unit is excellent
reviews.reviewText: This outdoor heater lights up instantaneously and every time. The burner unit is excellent and works perfect. The instructions and packing are very good. The metal housing of the base and pole are a little flimsy as is the top reflector. Not heavy material and I doubt it is stainless steel under the color paint. We’ll see how it holds up over the winter outside. This replaced a very well built all stainless steel unit that was over ten years old and looked new although the burner unit wouldnt light. Wish this company had an all stainless heavy duty base, pole support and top.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought 2 of these for my patio and they work great. Easy to assemble, comes with good instructions.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Works like a charm,fast starting and reliable

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice value for a patio heater
reviews.reviewText: The manufacturer (East Oak) did a great job of packaging all the parts and making assembly very easy. I fired it up and was pleasantly surprised out how much heat it put out. This isn’t a heavy duty restaurant grade patio heater but it works fine and was cheap.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Dangerous Product - Propane System Defective Out of the Box
reviews.reviewText: Extremely disappointed with this purchase. I had purchased it for a holiday party and put it together about a week before the party, only to find that the propane valve did not work, and was actually quite dangerous. When you push the valve down to light the pilot, the whole thing Explodes into a fireball because instead of triggering the pilot, it triggers the valve on high. I tried multiple times, and multiple different people to rectify the situation, and the valve was indeed defective. I contacted the company because there was no option to return it to Amazon, and the only options the company gave me were a credit to PayPal or an Amazon credit. Would not recommend this product or purchase again. Unless I want to be injured or burnt.
